# Elden Ring Builds Checklist Project Rules

1. Feature-first organization - all new features go in src/features/
2. Use TypeScript for all new code
3. Tailwind for styling - no CSS modules
4. Components follow Container/Presenter pattern
5. Custom hooks for shared logic
6. Prisma for all database operations
7. Mobile-first responsive design
8. Error handling with proper user feedback
9. Accessibility is a priority
10. Keep components small and focused
